          "policy_name": "EBS - consider upgrading gp2 volumes to gp3",
          "policy_slug": "aws-gp2-to-gp3",
          "policy_message": "gp3 volumes are the latest generation of general-purpose SSD-based EBS volumes that enable you to provision performance independent of storage capacity, while providing up to **20% lower price per GB** than existing gp2 volumes. With gp3 volumes, you can scale IOPS (input/output operations per second) and throughput without needing to provision additional block storage capacity. This means you only pay for the storage you need.",
